112
113const char *
114clockname(
115 int num
116 )
117{
118 register struct clktype *clk;
119
120 for (clk = clktypes; clk->code != -1; clk++) {
121 if (num == clk->code)
122 return (clk->abbrev);
123 }
124 return (NULL);
125}
